Ensure that each room/home is using a different resref door
Resref: ds_rental_1 (rental_2, rental_3)

Ensure that the tag of the door follows this convention:
Tag: [area tag]_house_a2 (house_b2, house_c2)

In the case of rental homes, follow this convention for area transition:
Destination: [area tag]_house_a1 (house_b1, house_c1)

NAMING CONVENTIONS:

Rental Homes
----------------
The name of this door MUST be one of the following:
Rental Home, Large
Rental Home, Medium
Rental Home, Small

Rental Rooms
----------------
The name of this door MUST be one of the following:
Rental Room, Luxury
Rental Room, Deluxe
Rental Room, Basic
